| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4432 — Recovery Inhibition (metaencryptor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: acad2486-87d7-5659-bc36-965d5058c87c"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
